          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0416P1_20040121_WH_27'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-dawn-primarolo' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0416P1_20040121_WH_27' title='Link to this speech by Ms Dawn Primarolo' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
